## Installation

:::: tabs
::: tab npm
```sh
npm install nuggies@latest
```
:::
::: tab yarn
```sh
yarn add nuggies
```
:::
:::::

## Example

:::: tabs
::: tab connect.js

```js
const Nuggies = require('nuggies');
/*
MONGO_URI is your MongoDB connection URL.
*/
Nuggies.connect('MONGO_URI');
```

:::
::: tab giveaways.js

```js
const Nuggies = require('nuggies');

// Create
Nuggies.giveaways.create({
	message: message,
	prize: 'test',
	host: message.author.id,
	winners: 1,
	endAfter: '10s',
	requirements: {
		enabled: false,
	},
	channel: message.channel.id,
});

// Drop
Nuggies.giveaways.drop({
	message: message,
	prize: 'test',
	channel: message.channel.id,
	host: message.author.id,
});

// End
Nuggies.giveaways.end(message, data, giveawaymsg);

// startAgain
Nuggies.giveaways.startAgain(client);

// Reroll (async/await)
await Nuggies.giveaways.reroll(client, messageID);

// startTimer (async/await)
await Nuggies.giveaways.startTimer(message, data);

// GotoGiveaway (async/await)
await Nuggies.giveaways.gotoGiveaway(data);

// getByMessageID (async/await)
await Nuggies.giveaways.getByMessageID(messageID);
```

:::
::: tab buttonroles.js

```js
const Nuggies = require('nuggies');

const BUTTON_ROLES = new Nuggies.buttonroles().addrole({
	color: 'blurple',
	label: 'Nuggies',
	role: '781061040514269185',
});

Nuggies.buttonroles.create({
	message: message,
	role: BUTTON_ROLES,
	content: new Discord.MessageEmbed()
		.setTitle('Some Title')
		.setDescription('Some Description'),
	channelID: message.channel.id,
});
```

:::
::: tab dropdownroles.js

```js
const Nuggies = require('nuggies');

const DROP_DOWN_ROLES = new Nuggies.buttonroles().addrole({
	color: 'blurple',
	label: 'Nuggies',
	role: '781061040514269185',
});

Nuggies.dropdownroles.create({
	message: message,
	role: DROP_DOWN_ROLES,
	content: new Discord.MessageEmbed()
		.setTitle('Some Title')
		.setDescription('Some Description'),
	channelID: message.channel.id,
});
```

:::
::: tab interaction.js

```js
const Nuggies = require('nuggies');

// Other Libraries
const Discord = require('discord.js');
const client = new Discord.Client();
require('discord-buttons')(client);

client.on('clickButton', (button) => {
	Nuggies.buttonclick(client, button);
});

client.on('clickMenu', (menu) => {
	Nuggies.dropclick(client, menu);
});
```
